1. Turn off your internet connection.
2. Search your application’s name, and click open file location.
3. Again right-click & open file location.
4. Search for the file AMT, then open it.
5. Cut the file ‘application’ and paste it on Desktop.
6. Open the application file using Notepad
7. Search for the word ‘TRIALSERIALNUMBER’.
8. Change digits in the key with any other random digits. 
9. Save and paste it back in AMT File folder.